duTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 3, "EnglishDescription": "You may then go for offering the namaz. For each rakat of namaz that you offer near the tomb, you will have the reward of one who went 1000 times on Hajj and 1000 times on Umrah, manumitted 1000 slaves for the sake of Allah, and stood in the line of a missioned Prophet 1000 times.”", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Iske baad Imam Husain ke qubbe ke neeche namaz padhe keh wahan adaa ki gayi har rakat ke badle mein woh sawaab hai keh goya us ne 1000 Hajj aur 1000 Umrah anjaam diya ho, Raahe Khuda mein 1000 ghulaam azaad kiya ho aur Nabiye Mursal (s) ke ham-raah rahe kar 1000 martaba jehaad kiya ho.", "UrduDescription": "اس کے بعد نماز پڑھے کہ وہاں بجا لائی گئی ہر رکعت کے عوض اسے اس شخص جتنا ثواب ملے گا جو ۱۰۰۰ حج و عمرہ بجا لا چکا ہو ۱۰۰۰ غلام آزاد کیا ہو اور کسی پیغمبر ؐمرسل کے ہمراہ رہ کر ۱۰۰۰ مرتبہ جہاد کیا ہو۔ ", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": nu